Get IMGTHLA releases from GitHub

hla_releases.Rd

Retrieve the tags from the ANHIG/IMGTHLA repo and get the associated release names.

Usage

hla_releases(overwrite = FALSE)

Arguments

overwrite

Overwrite the existing tags.json file in getOption("hlabud_dir") with a new one from the IMGTHLA GitHub repo.

Value

A character vector of release names like "3.51.0"

Examples

# \donttest{
hla_releases() 
#>  [1] "3.52.0"   "3.51.0"   "3.50.0"   "3.49.0"   "3.48.0"   "3.47.0"  
#>  [7] "3.46.0"   "3.45.1"   "3.45.01"  "3.45.0.1" "3.45.0"   "3.44.1"  
#> [13] "3.44.0"   "3.43.0"   "3.42.0"   "3.41.2"   "3.41.0"   "3.40.0"  
#> [19] "3.39.0"   "3.38.0"   "3.37.0"   "3.36.0"   "3.35.0"   "3.34.0"  
#> [25] "3.33.0"   "3.32.0"   "3.31.0"   "3.30.0"   "3.29.0"   "3.28.0"  
# }
